WEBVTT

00:02:31.704 --> 00:02:34.308
[NARRATOR] All pirates searching
for the treasure One Piece

00:02:34.342 --> 00:02:36.947
must brave the second half
of the Grand Line.

00:02:36.980 --> 00:02:41.289
These wild and dangerous seas
are known as the New World.

00:02:41.322 --> 00:02:44.295
Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
a boy whose body became rubber

00:02:44.328 --> 00:02:45.865
after eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,

00:02:45.899 --> 00:02:49.371
sets sail into the New World
with his faithful crew.

00:02:49.405 --> 00:02:53.680
I'm gonna be the
King of the Pirates!

00:02:55.818 --> 00:02:57.187
[NARRATOR]
In order to defeat one of the

00:02:57.220 --> 00:02:59.125
Four Emperors of the New World,

00:02:59.158 --> 00:03:01.195
the Straw Hats form
an alliance with Law.

00:03:01.229 --> 00:03:03.734
Their current objective
is to destroy a man-made

00:03:03.767 --> 00:03:06.272
Devil Fruit Factory in
the kingdom of Dressrosa.

00:03:06.305 --> 00:03:07.709
As the Straw Hats do battle with

00:03:07.743 --> 00:03:10.146
the fierce fighters of
the Don Quixote Family,

00:03:10.180 --> 00:03:12.151
Luffy and Law rush
to the royal palace

00:03:12.184 --> 00:03:14.288
to take down Doflamingo himself.

00:03:14.321 --> 00:03:17.562
And for Law, it turns out
the fight was personal.

00:03:17.595 --> 00:03:20.267
Law has had a complicated
past with Doflamingo,

00:03:20.300 --> 00:03:21.770
and his brother Corazon.

00:03:21.803 --> 00:03:26.345
Their connection began with
a twist of fate 16 years ago.

00:03:26.379 --> 00:03:30.855
[LAW]
It's Trafalgar D. Water Law.

00:03:30.889 --> 00:03:32.491
The "D." is secret.

00:03:32.525 --> 00:03:35.598
My true name is Water.
For generations, my family...

00:03:35.632 --> 00:03:38.504
[LAW gasps]
H-Hey, what are you doing?

00:03:38.537 --> 00:03:41.008
What's the big deal, Corazon?

00:03:42.244 --> 00:03:45.986
What you just said. Was it true?

00:03:46.019 --> 00:03:48.456
Your secret name's "D."?

00:03:48.490 --> 00:03:51.964
If that's right, you need to
get the hell outta here.

00:03:51.997 --> 00:03:53.834
Away from Doffy.

00:03:54.803 --> 00:03:56.305
Law! Listen.

00:03:56.339 --> 00:03:58.110
You cannot be around him.

00:03:58.143 --> 00:04:00.480
You have to get out of here!

00:04:03.419 --> 00:04:05.290
[LUFFY]
"A Rocky Road!

00:04:05.323 --> 00:04:08.697
Law and Corazon's
Journey of Life!"

00:04:20.922 --> 00:04:24.596
You're talking?
Since when can you speak?

00:04:27.969 --> 00:04:29.639
Always could.

00:04:32.645 --> 00:04:36.587
You mean, you've lied to
your brother this whole time?

00:04:36.620 --> 00:04:39.793
I never once indicated
to him that I became mute.

00:04:39.826 --> 00:04:42.599
That is a crazy assumption
the guy made on his own.

00:04:42.632 --> 00:04:44.769
That's lying!
What's wrong with you?

00:04:44.803 --> 00:04:46.507
You're being deceitful
by not correcting him!

00:04:46.540 --> 00:04:50.548
[ROSINANTE]
Whoa, whoa, whoa. Silence, now!

00:04:56.894 --> 00:04:59.766
[inaudible]

00:04:59.800 --> 00:05:03.974
[LAW gasps]
What the hell happened?

00:05:08.584 --> 00:05:11.155
[gasps] All the sound stopped!

00:05:11.189 --> 00:05:14.261
Where'd it go? How?

00:05:14.295 --> 00:05:16.165
It looks like
people are talking,

00:05:16.199 --> 00:05:17.868
but I can't hear anything!

00:05:17.902 --> 00:05:21.108
[ROSINANTE] You were being loud,
so took a counter measure.

00:05:21.142 --> 00:05:22.779
They can't hear us.

00:05:22.812 --> 00:05:26.186
Just like how you can't
hear a peep from outside.

00:05:26.219 --> 00:05:29.124
I put up a sound-proof
wall to cover us.

00:05:31.261 --> 00:05:33.700
You won't see it.
It's invisible.

00:05:40.581 --> 00:05:44.055
I ate the Calm-Calm Fruit
and became a silent man.

00:05:44.088 --> 00:05:45.390
[gasps]

00:05:49.398 --> 00:05:52.037
[LAW]
You have Devil Fruit powers?

00:05:56.613 --> 00:06:00.220
[LAW] Y-You're insane!
It's all been a lie?

00:06:00.253 --> 00:06:03.694
Wait a sec. You faked the
accidents, too, didn't you?

00:06:03.727 --> 00:06:08.604
[ROSINANTE chuckles] That's
right. You're a sharp cookie.

00:06:10.073 --> 00:06:11.576
The whole clutz thing is an act.

00:06:11.609 --> 00:06:14.582
You caught on fire
again, you liar!

00:06:23.399 --> 00:06:26.405
I've been clumsy my whole life,
that won't change.

00:06:26.439 --> 00:06:27.775
There. Y'happy now?

00:06:27.808 --> 00:06:28.944
Gimme a break!

00:06:28.978 --> 00:06:31.816
You mean to tell me,
that's the only truth to you?

00:06:31.850 --> 00:06:34.722
Why are you hiding all this
crap from your friends?

00:06:34.756 --> 00:06:36.593
[ROSINANTE]
They're not my friends.

00:06:36.626 --> 00:06:39.766
I'm with them,
but not by choice.

00:06:39.799 --> 00:06:43.339
Someone's gotta curb
my brother Doffy's rampage.

00:06:43.373 --> 00:06:45.176
It's hard to believe
we're related.

00:06:45.210 --> 00:06:48.884
Our parents showed us
nothing but love, after all.

00:06:55.631 --> 00:06:59.037
[ROSINANTE] But that monster
has no humanity.

00:07:10.795 --> 00:07:15.470
[ROSINANTE crying]
Help me!

00:07:15.504 --> 00:07:18.276
Please, my boys are innocent!

00:07:18.309 --> 00:07:21.282
Direct your arrows
at me, not them!

00:07:21.316 --> 00:07:22.685
I beg you!

00:07:22.719 --> 00:07:25.123
Please don't harm
my children anymore!

00:07:25.156 --> 00:07:26.693
[ROSINANTE cries]

00:07:26.727 --> 00:07:32.170
Help, Daddy, it hurts
everywhere! I wanna die!

00:07:40.286 --> 00:07:42.123
[TOWNSMEN gasp]

00:07:46.833 --> 00:07:50.273
[DOFLAMINGO]
You'll pay for this.

00:07:50.307 --> 00:07:53.212
I'll get even. I swear it!

00:07:53.245 --> 00:07:54.414
[HOMING gasps]

00:07:54.448 --> 00:07:55.483
Doffy, no.

00:07:55.517 --> 00:07:59.257
You wretches!
I won't die today!

00:08:03.534 --> 00:08:07.509
I swear to survive whatever
torment you throw at me!

00:08:07.542 --> 00:08:09.646
Remember my words!

00:08:09.679 --> 00:08:12.685
I look forward to the day
that I hunt you down

00:08:12.718 --> 00:08:16.258
and murder every
single one of you!

00:08:20.734 --> 00:08:22.070
[ROSINANTE]
He's dangerous.

00:08:22.104 --> 00:08:25.911
My brother's innately wicked
nature knows no bounds.

00:08:27.782 --> 00:08:29.719
[ROSINANTE] The only people
who have seen the full extent

00:08:29.752 --> 00:08:34.194
of his brutality are the
four Executives, including me,

00:08:34.227 --> 00:08:37.902
and the first Corazon, Vergo.

00:08:37.935 --> 00:08:38.937
Who's Vergo?

00:08:38.970 --> 00:08:41.209
An extremely
powerful individual.

00:08:41.242 --> 00:08:44.916
Right now he's away from the
Family on a secret operation.

00:08:44.949 --> 00:08:47.755
But the details of that
are between him and Doffy.

00:08:47.789 --> 00:08:51.563
That guy has nothing to do
with you, so forget about him.

00:08:52.264 --> 00:08:53.534
[ROSINANTE]
Listen, Law.

00:08:53.567 --> 00:08:56.005
You can't turn into
a monster like my brother.

00:08:56.039 --> 00:08:57.608
Now scram. Quickly.

00:08:57.642 --> 00:08:59.345
[LAW]
No way! I'm not leaving!

00:08:59.378 --> 00:09:02.083
That's exactly what I wanna be!

00:09:02.985 --> 00:09:05.791
[inaudible]

00:09:05.825 --> 00:09:07.796
Hm?

00:09:07.829 --> 00:09:11.202
[ROSINANTE] Look. You possess
the secret name of "D."

00:09:11.235 --> 00:09:12.638
You realize what that means?

00:09:12.671 --> 00:09:14.375
You're a part of a fateful few.

00:09:14.408 --> 00:09:17.948
Growing up, when children
misbehaved, we were told,

00:09:17.982 --> 00:09:22.090
"If you don't fall in line,
you'll be eaten alive by D."

00:09:24.595 --> 00:09:26.031
[ROSINANTE]
Every so often, another person

00:09:26.065 --> 00:09:29.137
with "D." in their name
would gain public attention.

00:09:29.171 --> 00:09:34.749
And you'd overhear the elderly
making passing comments like,

00:09:34.783 --> 00:09:38.223
"D. will surely
bring a new storm."

00:09:38.256 --> 00:09:39.660
The hell's that mean?

00:09:39.693 --> 00:09:42.298
You're trying to say
I'm a monster, then?

00:09:42.331 --> 00:09:43.834
[ROSINANTE]
Perhaps.

00:09:46.371 --> 00:09:48.076
The details are still unknown,

00:09:48.109 --> 00:09:50.547
but that name's
survived for centuries

00:09:50.581 --> 00:09:53.486
and has been muttered
across the entire world.

00:09:53.520 --> 00:09:54.855
One more thing.

00:09:54.889 --> 00:09:56.827
Those who fear
the inheritors of D.

00:09:56.860 --> 00:09:59.331
have given them another title.

00:10:02.772 --> 00:10:04.643
"Sworn enemy of gods"!

00:10:04.676 --> 00:10:05.911
[LAW gasps]

00:10:10.420 --> 00:10:11.890
[LAW]
Gods?

00:10:11.923 --> 00:10:14.729
[ROSINANTE] If Celestial Dragons
are "gods" in this analogy,

00:10:14.763 --> 00:10:16.900
the purpose of
your people might be

00:10:16.933 --> 00:10:19.872
the "destruction of this world."

00:10:21.643 --> 00:10:23.078
But look.

00:10:23.112 --> 00:10:26.853
This meaning of "destruction"
is different than Doffy's.

00:10:26.886 --> 00:10:30.827
It's a force that opposes
the order of heaven itself.

00:10:36.506 --> 00:10:38.577
Why're you spouting
this crap at me?

00:10:38.610 --> 00:10:40.982
I joined your dumb Family
for one purpose.

00:10:41.015 --> 00:10:42.885
To kill people before I die!

00:10:42.919 --> 00:10:44.956
Don't assume I wanna
work for you!

00:10:44.989 --> 00:10:47.360
I only answer to Doflamingo.

00:10:47.393 --> 00:10:48.864
What would I wanna leave for?

00:10:48.897 --> 00:10:51.302
I'm just gonna die
in a year anyway!

00:10:51.335 --> 00:10:53.473
There's gotta be a cure
out there somewhere.

00:10:53.507 --> 00:10:57.816
Shut up! I'm so ratting
you out, sucker!

00:10:57.849 --> 00:10:59.685
Doflamingo'll be angry!

00:10:59.719 --> 00:11:01.623
Hey, wait!

00:11:01.657 --> 00:11:03.827
Bet he freaks out when
he learns you can talk!

00:11:03.860 --> 00:11:06.365
[ROSINANTE]
You damn brat!

00:11:06.398 --> 00:11:07.835
[gasps]

00:11:07.868 --> 00:11:09.170
[ROSINANTE gasps]

00:11:10.875 --> 00:11:14.716
I'm way stronger than
two years ago! Later, jerk!

00:11:14.750 --> 00:11:16.118
[ROSINANTE shrieks]

00:11:17.287 --> 00:11:20.894
You moron! You broke the
"Blood Law" a second time!

00:11:20.928 --> 00:11:22.699
Hey. Why were you
moving your mouths,

00:11:22.732 --> 00:11:24.936
but not saying anything?

00:11:26.105 --> 00:11:28.242
[LAW] I'll buy you both ice
cream if you shut up about it.

00:11:28.276 --> 00:11:31.616
[BUFFALO] Really? I'll take
a 500-Berry, King size cone!

00:11:31.650 --> 00:11:33.420
[LAW]
Baby 5, can you spot me?

00:11:33.453 --> 00:11:35.958
[BABY 5]
Huh? O-Okay!

00:11:35.992 --> 00:11:40.199
Oh my gosh, he really
needs me for something!

00:11:52.023 --> 00:11:54.027
[ROSINANTE]
My time's up.

00:12:01.943 --> 00:12:05.450
[ROSINANTE] Dammit! I shouldn't
have trusted that kid.

00:12:05.483 --> 00:12:07.588
I screwed up, royally.

00:12:08.422 --> 00:12:11.061
[ROSINANTE] I don't think
Doffy's made it back yet.

00:12:11.094 --> 00:12:14.869
I should have just enough time
to pack my crap and book it.

00:12:16.606 --> 00:12:18.577
[DOFLAMINGO]
Corazon!

00:12:18.610 --> 00:12:19.879
[ROSINANTE]
What?

00:12:26.025 --> 00:12:28.863
[ROSINANTE]
Dammit. He's already here.

00:12:36.012 --> 00:12:37.749
Took ya long enough.

00:12:37.782 --> 00:12:39.418
We're about to set sail.

00:12:39.451 --> 00:12:41.422
The Navy's on our tail again.

00:12:41.455 --> 00:12:43.860
Tsuru's on her way. We gotta go.

00:12:43.893 --> 00:12:46.031
C'mon, haul ass!

00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:50.273
[ROSINANTE]
Hasn't he said anything yet?

00:12:50.306 --> 00:12:52.945
[LAW chuckles]

00:12:55.651 --> 00:12:59.158
Heheh. I decided not to tell.

00:12:59.191 --> 00:13:01.428
I gave it some thought
and remembered

00:13:01.461 --> 00:13:05.069
that I owed you for keeping
quiet back when I stabbed you.

00:13:05.103 --> 00:13:07.340
I'd call that about even.

00:13:07.373 --> 00:13:09.845
[LAW chuckles]

00:13:16.760 --> 00:13:19.297
[DOFLAMINGO]
Hey! I said hurry it up!

00:13:19.331 --> 00:13:21.068
What are you doing?

00:13:29.151 --> 00:13:34.028
[DIAMANTE]
Corazon's missing! Corazon!

00:13:34.061 --> 00:13:36.465
Anyone seen him or Law?

00:13:36.499 --> 00:13:38.202
[LAO G]
What?

00:13:38.235 --> 00:13:40.340
[GLADIUS] I swear I
saw them board together.

00:13:40.373 --> 00:13:41.543
They aren't here?

00:13:41.576 --> 00:13:43.880
What are we chatting about?

00:13:45.651 --> 00:13:49.091
We need the extra fire power
and I can't find either of them!

00:13:49.124 --> 00:13:51.428
And I looked everywhere!

00:13:52.264 --> 00:13:56.071
Young Master! Found this
in Corazon's hammock.

00:13:57.240 --> 00:13:59.746
[SEÃ‘OR] Looks like they
took off together.

00:13:59.779 --> 00:14:02.350
What the hell is he thinking?

00:14:02.383 --> 00:14:07.360
[LAW grunting]

00:14:07.394 --> 00:14:09.031
Untie me right now!

00:14:09.064 --> 00:14:11.836
Do you realize you
just kidnapped me?

00:14:11.870 --> 00:14:13.707
Corazon! You creep!

00:14:13.741 --> 00:14:14.975
You'll pay for this!

00:14:15.009 --> 00:14:17.882
Say something!
I know you can talk!

00:14:17.915 --> 00:14:19.885
Hey, pick up that
Transponder Snail!

00:14:19.919 --> 00:14:21.455
It's Doflamingo, isn't it?

00:14:21.488 --> 00:14:22.825
I'll talk, just pick it up!

00:14:22.859 --> 00:14:24.996
Come on! Pick it up!

00:14:25.029 --> 00:14:28.804
What's wrong with you?
Doflamingo! Help!

00:14:28.837 --> 00:14:33.445
What're you gonna do to me?

00:15:04.208 --> 00:15:07.748
[beeping]

00:15:07.781 --> 00:15:09.953
Are you calling up Doflamingo?

00:15:09.986 --> 00:15:12.156
Hey! Come and rescue me!

00:15:12.190 --> 00:15:13.126
[TRANSPONDER SNAIL A]
Cu-lick.

00:15:13.159 --> 00:15:15.931
[SENGOKU]
Rice crackers!

00:15:15.964 --> 00:15:18.504
Cookies. It's me.

00:15:18.537 --> 00:15:20.875
[SENGOKU]
Oh, Rosinante.

00:15:20.908 --> 00:15:23.680
Hey, uh. Need some time off.

00:15:33.332 --> 00:15:34.868
[SENGOKU]
You run into trouble?

00:15:34.902 --> 00:15:36.338
[ROSINANTE]
It's a personal matter.

00:15:36.371 --> 00:15:39.344
[SENGOKU] I see, understood.
How are the little ones doing?

00:15:39.378 --> 00:15:42.384
Think you can
scare them off soon?

00:15:42.417 --> 00:15:44.989
[ROSINANTE]
I think those three are staying.

00:15:45.023 --> 00:15:47.795
[SENGOKU] That Family's
becoming infamous now.

00:15:47.829 --> 00:15:50.000
Take extra caution.

00:15:50.033 --> 00:15:51.502
[ROSINANTE]
Will do.

00:15:54.041 --> 00:15:55.343
[SENGOKU]
Do as you see fit.

00:15:55.376 --> 00:15:57.882
I wholeheartedly
entrust this case to you.

00:15:57.915 --> 00:15:59.618
Just keep me updated.

00:15:59.652 --> 00:16:02.859
Roger that. I'll send you
a detailed report.

00:16:02.892 --> 00:16:04.562
Cu-lick.

00:16:14.782 --> 00:16:16.686
[MARINE A]
Admiral Sengoku!

00:16:16.719 --> 00:16:19.357
The officer who asked
for reassignment is here.

00:16:19.390 --> 00:16:21.494
[SENGOKU]
Yes, yes. Send him in.

00:16:24.400 --> 00:16:26.138
[SENGOKU]
You wanted to see me?

00:16:26.171 --> 00:16:28.376
I've heard a lot about you.

00:16:28.409 --> 00:16:30.514
You've had quite
a successful first year

00:16:30.547 --> 00:16:33.686
and have been turning
a lot of heads.

00:16:36.291 --> 00:16:39.064
[SENGOKU] You wish to
transfer to G-5, correct?

00:16:39.098 --> 00:16:40.332
What was your name?

00:16:40.366 --> 00:16:43.774
Also, FYI, there's half
an egg on your cheek.

00:16:43.807 --> 00:16:46.211
[VERGO]
Sir! Name's Vergo!

00:16:48.817 --> 00:16:50.755
[LAW]
Who'd you call just now?

00:16:50.788 --> 00:16:52.256
Did you say "report"?

00:16:52.290 --> 00:16:53.827
You been hiding something?

00:16:53.860 --> 00:16:55.396
Are you working with the Navy?

00:16:55.430 --> 00:16:56.867
[ROSINANTE]
Got something against 'em?

00:16:56.900 --> 00:16:59.572
The Government and
their allies sicken me!

00:16:59.605 --> 00:17:01.275
Well, I ain't no Marine.

00:17:01.308 --> 00:17:02.711
[LAW]
Is that a lie?

00:17:02.744 --> 00:17:07.287
I won't go to the hospital!
Come on! Stop carrying me!

00:17:07.320 --> 00:17:10.894
You're acting like every other
brat in the world, Law.

00:17:10.927 --> 00:17:13.332
I'll go to every
hospital if I have to.

00:17:13.365 --> 00:17:16.205
I'll find a cure
for your sickness.

00:17:16.238 --> 00:17:19.778
Look how big this one is.
I bet they can fix ya up.

00:17:20.647 --> 00:17:23.218
[DOCTOR A]
Huh? Get that kid outta here!

00:17:23.252 --> 00:17:25.189
You can't catch
White Lead Disease.

00:17:25.223 --> 00:17:27.493
Isn't there any
medicine for it yet?

00:17:27.528 --> 00:17:31.536
[DOCTOR A] M-M-M-Might I ask,
where were you born?

00:17:31.569 --> 00:17:32.805
I'm from Flevance.

00:17:32.838 --> 00:17:34.140
[DOCTORS]
That's the White Town!

00:17:34.174 --> 00:17:36.913
No! I dun' wanna get sick!

00:17:36.946 --> 00:17:38.116
Get it together!

00:17:38.149 --> 00:17:40.386
We need antiseptic gloves
and a gas mask!

00:17:40.420 --> 00:17:44.227
Call security and notify
the government! Pronto!

00:17:44.261 --> 00:17:45.664
[DOCTOR E]
No, no!

00:17:45.698 --> 00:17:47.066
[LAW]
Forget it!

00:17:47.100 --> 00:17:48.168
[ROSINANTE]
Law!

00:17:48.201 --> 00:17:50.741
See that? I'm sub-human to them!

00:17:50.774 --> 00:17:53.846
[DOCTORS crying]

00:17:57.453 --> 00:17:59.391
Please leave us alone,
you White Monster!

00:17:59.424 --> 00:18:01.461
We don't want your
gross disease! Go away!

00:18:01.495 --> 00:18:04.134
[DOCTOR A] How dare you bring
that infected little creature

00:18:04.167 --> 00:18:05.971
into a hospital of all places!

00:18:06.005 --> 00:18:08.476
Do you realize you're putting
hundreds of patients at risk?

00:18:08.510 --> 00:18:10.446
[HOSPITAL STAFF A] This is an
emergency announcement.

00:18:10.479 --> 00:18:12.183
A patient with
White Lead Disease

00:18:12.217 --> 00:18:14.621
is loose in the hospital.

00:18:28.717 --> 00:18:31.354
[DOCTOR A] The big one's
a dangerous freak, too!

00:18:31.387 --> 00:18:34.595
[HOSPITAL STAFF A] All wards
prepare for sterilization.

00:18:35.329 --> 00:18:38.503
Forget that hospital!
I'm real sorry.

00:18:38.536 --> 00:18:41.208
Hope that didn't hit
a sore spot on ya, kid.

00:18:41.241 --> 00:18:45.884
I told you! I didn't
want to see a doctor!

00:18:45.917 --> 00:18:48.255
Not all doctors suck like him.

00:18:48.289 --> 00:18:50.827
I'm positive we'll find a good
one at this next hospital.

00:18:50.861 --> 00:18:53.198
[LAW]
Don't force me to go!

00:18:53.231 --> 00:18:54.602
[DOCTOR B]
He should be put down!

00:18:54.636 --> 00:18:57.206
That's a severe case of
that White Lead Disease!

00:18:57.240 --> 00:18:59.077
Take him away before
he dooms us all!

00:18:59.111 --> 00:19:01.281
[HOSPITAL STAFF screaming]

00:19:01.315 --> 00:19:03.318
[ROSINANTE] Change of plans.
Let's try the next one.

00:19:03.351 --> 00:19:05.423
[LAW]
Enough! I'm tired of this!

00:19:05.456 --> 00:19:07.460
We've got an emergency! Help!

00:19:07.493 --> 00:19:09.063
There's a Flevance survivor.

00:19:09.097 --> 00:19:10.835
You were supposed to
purge 'em all!

00:19:10.868 --> 00:19:13.305
What is wrong with you?!

00:19:13.338 --> 00:19:16.746
Look, Law! The people
around here seem kind-hearted!

00:19:16.779 --> 00:19:17.814
[LAW]
No!

00:19:17.848 --> 00:19:20.587
Keep those filthy white
blotches away from us!

00:19:20.620 --> 00:19:21.723
[DOCTORS scream]

00:19:21.756 --> 00:19:25.764
[ROSINANTE] Screw you, buddy!
You're no doctor!

00:19:25.797 --> 00:19:27.535
[NEWSCASTER A] Eight hospitals
have been hit as a boy

00:19:27.568 --> 00:19:29.203
with White Lead Disease
terrorizes the--

00:19:29.237 --> 00:19:32.210
[LAW]
Give up. I'm getting sicker.

00:19:32.243 --> 00:19:34.381
I can't take anymore!

00:19:34.414 --> 00:19:35.851
Shut up!

00:19:35.885 --> 00:19:37.187
We'll find the cure.

00:19:37.220 --> 00:19:38.624
You're not gonna die.

00:19:38.657 --> 00:19:42.196
This next one will
help you. Don't give up.

00:19:42.229 --> 00:19:43.833
[TOWNSMAN A]
White Lead Disease!

00:19:43.866 --> 00:19:46.138
[TOWNSMAN B]
Put the hospital on lock down!

00:19:46.171 --> 00:19:47.508
I'm gonna kick your ass!

00:19:47.541 --> 00:19:49.077
This kiddo needs your help!

00:19:49.111 --> 00:19:54.320
I've had enough! Corazon!

00:20:08.315 --> 00:20:11.689
[sighs, hiccups]

00:20:13.225 --> 00:20:15.462
[ROSINANTE]
What the hell am I doing?

00:20:16.364 --> 00:20:18.268
[ROSINANTE] I've been forcing
this poor kid to relive

00:20:18.301 --> 00:20:22.578
his horrible childhood
over and over again.

00:20:22.611 --> 00:20:25.016
He's not getting
any better either.

00:20:25.751 --> 00:20:28.624
[ROSINANTE] I wondered it if was
the Will of D. driving me,

00:20:28.657 --> 00:20:31.962
but no, I don't care
about that anymore!

00:20:35.537 --> 00:20:36.639
[ROSINANTE]
I just...

00:20:36.673 --> 00:20:39.611
I just feel so sorry
for this damn kid!

00:20:41.549 --> 00:20:43.251
Law!

00:20:46.593 --> 00:20:50.499
[ROSINANTE] Knowing you,
you'd hate to hear this,

00:20:50.534 --> 00:20:52.370
but this blubbering idiot

00:20:52.403 --> 00:20:55.777
is trying everything
he can to save you.

00:20:57.681 --> 00:21:01.187
[ROSINANTE] You're still
a pain in the ass kid.

00:21:01.221 --> 00:21:03.693
But hearing you
talk about death...

00:21:04.762 --> 00:21:07.968
[ROSINANTE]
My heart can't take it.

00:21:10.472 --> 00:21:14.748
[ROSINANTE] You may have stabbed
me, you little shit. But...

00:21:17.220 --> 00:21:19.926
It didn't hurt at all.

00:21:19.959 --> 00:21:24.200
You were the one who was
actually suffering back then.

00:21:24.234 --> 00:21:26.839
I just wanted to
fix things for you.

00:21:26.873 --> 00:21:28.408
Law.

00:21:38.328 --> 00:21:39.932
--[thud]
--[ROSINANTE groans]

00:21:47.046 --> 00:21:50.119
[ROSINANTE snores]

00:21:50.152 --> 00:21:53.693
[LAW]
Cora. Hey, Cora!

00:21:54.561 --> 00:21:56.733
Get up, oaf, breakfast is done.

00:21:56.766 --> 00:21:59.037
[ROSINANTE gasps]

00:21:59.070 --> 00:22:01.442
What's that face for?

00:22:01.475 --> 00:22:03.178
You called me "Cora"?

00:22:03.212 --> 00:22:04.548
You said that. Yeah?

00:22:04.582 --> 00:22:06.986
Ya want the food? Or not?

00:22:15.938 --> 00:22:17.439
[LAW]
Cora!

00:22:18.375 --> 00:22:20.680
[LAW grunts]

00:22:22.082 --> 00:22:24.755
[LAW] I won't ever forget
the compassion you showed me

00:22:24.788 --> 00:22:27.227
when the world
turned its back on me.

00:22:27.260 --> 00:22:29.531
[DOFLAMINGO chuckles]

00:22:31.201 --> 00:22:33.038
[LAW yells]

00:22:38.081 --> 00:22:40.887
[BELLAMY yells]

00:22:44.561 --> 00:22:47.200
Run, Straw Hat.
Ya can't save me!

00:22:47.233 --> 00:22:48.368
[LUFFY]
Bellamy, stop!

00:22:48.402 --> 00:22:52.176
[DOFLAMINGO chuckles]
This is it.

00:22:52.210 --> 00:22:56.552
Playtime's over.
Fun while it lasted.

00:23:01.327 --> 00:23:03.498
[BELLAMY yells]

00:23:03.532 --> 00:23:05.637
See you in hell!

00:23:06.538 --> 00:23:09.544
[LUFFY screams]

00:23:14.254 --> 00:23:17.026
[NARRATOR] With little time left
to find a cure for young Law,

00:23:17.059 --> 00:23:19.565
Corazon recklessly
pulls a drastic measure

00:23:19.598 --> 00:23:22.369
while making enemies out of
nearly everyone in the process.

00:23:22.403 --> 00:23:26.177
Putting his own life at risk,
Corazon steals the Op-Op Fruit,

00:23:26.211 --> 00:23:29.585
in a desperate attempt
to reverse Law's condition.

00:23:29.619 --> 00:23:31.421
[LUFFY]
On the next One Piece!

00:23:31.454 --> 00:23:35.129
"The Time Is Ticking Down!
Seize the Op-Op Fruit!"

00:23:35.162 --> 00:23:37.867
I'm gonna be
King of the Pirates!

